The manufacturer shall declare one of the following:
1)	The equipment class for the equipment under test, as defined in the IEC 60 721-3-3 [7];
2)	The equipment class for the equipment under test, as defined in the IEC 60 721-3-4 [8];
3)	The equipment that does not comply with the mentioned classes, the relevant classes from IEC 60 721 [9] documentation for temperature, humidity and vibration shall be declared.
NOTE:	Reduced functionality for conditions that fall outside of the standard operational conditions is not tested in the present document. These may be stated and tested separately.
